name: Jennifer Lising Roxas
text: I love science, research and mentoring...so I know I'll be a bit miserable if I can't work...  Pero I'll have more time with my kids, gardening, cooking, painting the house, and volunteering. I'll revisit music and arts. I'll read non-science literature (kung bawal talaga na related sa current job).
